title: [Fhorian Village, Storage Shed]
description: Soft tendrils of moonlight poke through the cracks in the wall, illuminating thick curtains of cobwebs hanging from the rafters.  A pile of straw in one corner hints that someone may have lived here at one time -- but that must have been years ago, judging from the heavy layer of dust that covers everything.
